+  function sendRequestsSequentially(urls) {
+    let index = 0;

+    function sendNextRequest() {
+      return $.ajax({
+        url: urls[index],
+        type: 'GET',
+      }).then(response => {
+        return Promise.resolve(response);
+      }).catch(() => {
+        index++;

-"<b>Auto CDN IP</b> mode: It is like cdn mode, except that the appropriate ip is automatically set based on the ip provided by ircf.space. In auto_cdn_ip  the ip will be resolved from domain but in cdn mode the domain will be returned<br>\n"

+"<b>CDN</b> Mode: choose this mode if you use your server's domain on a CDN provider. (Proxy Mode On)<br>\n"
+"<b>Auto CDN IP</b> Mode: It is like CDN mode, except that the appropriate IP is automatically set based on the IP provided by ircf.space. In Auto_CDN_IP  the IP will be resolved from domain but in cdn mode the domain will be returned<br>\n"
+"<b>Relay</b> Mode: choose this mode if you are using one or more Intermediary servers. <a href=\"https://github.com/hiddify/hiddify-config/discussions/129\" target=\"_blank\">Read More</a>\n"
